(35, 101, 'District of Columbia', 'Washington DC', NULL, '2021-10-04', '10:00:00', 'AM', '1320 Old Chain Bridge Rd, McLean, VA, USA', 'How To Buy A Home Zoom Class', '<hr />\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 20px 0px; min-height: 1px; font-size: 18px; line-height: 26.4px; font-family: proxima-nova, \'Open Sans\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: #ffffff;\">Would you like to buy a home this fall? We&nbsp;<strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px;\">specialize in helping</strong>&nbsp;<strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px;\">home buyers&nbsp;</strong>in Washington DC, Virginia, and Maryland including the Greater Baltimore &amp; Annapolis areas.</p>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 20px 0px; min-height: 1px; font-size: 18px; line-height: 26.4px; font-family: proxima-nova, \'Open Sans\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: #ffffff;\">Our home buying class is free, interactive, and available via Zoom.</p>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 20px 0px; min-height: 1px; font-size: 18px; line-height: 26.4px; font-family: proxima-nova, \'Open Sans\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: #ffffff;\">The home buying class will be led by&nbsp;<a style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 20px 0px; color: #009e13; text-decoration-line: none; font-size: 1.125rem; line-height: 26.4px;\" href=\"https://www.homesbuyhendersons.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\">Victoria, Marshall &amp; Cliff Henderson&nbsp;</a>experienced true buyer agents and members of the&nbsp;<a style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 20px 0px; color: #009e13; text-decoration-line: none; font-size: 1.125rem; line-height: 26.4px;\" href=\"https://naeba.org/listen-up-podcast/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px;\">National Association of Exclusive Buyer Agents.</strong></a></p>\r\n<p style