(3, 'How can I contribute as a local leader, nonprofit or other community organization on Patch?', 1, '<p><span style=\"color: #333333; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \'Segoe UI\', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; background-color: #ffffff;\">Are you a leader in your community? Do you serve your neighbors through a local group, nonprofit or other organization? If so, you are uniquely qualified to share important news and information with your community. Our platform offers you the opportunity to engage directly with the community you serve at no cost or obligation.&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: #333333; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \'Segoe UI\', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; background-color: #ffffff;\"><span class=\"wysiwyg-font-size-large\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-size: large;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">1.Help your community</strong></span></p>\r\n<div class=\"p-rich_text_section\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: #333333; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \'Segoe UI\', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; background-color: #ffffff;\">Raise awareness around your cause, initiative or other local services</div>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: #333333; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \'Segoe UI\', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; background-color: #ffffff;\"><span class=\"wysiwyg-font-size-large\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-size: large;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">2. Expand your reach</strong></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: #333333; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \'Segoe UI\', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; background-color: #ffffff;\">Share information about your organization or group; its mission, meeting times, etc.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: #333333; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \'Segoe UI\', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; background-color: #ffffff;\"><span class=\"wysiwyg-font-size-large\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-size: large;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">3. Make a local impact</strong></span></p>\r\n<div class=\"p-rich_text_section\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: #333333; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \'Segoe UI\', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; background-color: #ffffff;\">Show your support to fellow local leaders or community members&nbsp;Many local leaders and organizations just like you are already posting updates and sharing local resources on Patch. To get started engaging directly with your community:&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div class=\"p-rich_text_section\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: #333333; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \'Segoe UI\', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; background-color: #ffffff;\"><br style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\" /><span class=\"wysiwyg-font-size-large\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-size: large;\"><a class=\"c-link\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; background-color: transparent; color: #0072ef; text-decoration-line: none;\" href=\"https://www.patch.com/register\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Create your Patch profile here</a></span>.</div>\r\n<div class=\"p-rich_text_section\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: #333333; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \'Segoe UI\', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; background-color: #ffffff;\"><br style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\" />Once you&rsquo;ve created your profile, please&nbsp;<a class=\"c-link\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; background-color: transparent; color: #0072ef; text-decoration-line: none;\" href=\"https://docs.google.com/forms/d/e/1FAIpQLSdLLz6fRiui0Fwl1eN1CfINzuVXU1TxJbupwxTHcgFH_QtSiQ/viewform\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">fill out this form</a>&nbsp;so we can verify you as a local official.We look forward to adding you to the fast-growing group of key local leaders engaging with their communities on Patch.&nbsp;Do you work for any type of public agency? Then the&nbsp;<a class=\"c-link\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; background-color: transparent; color: #0072ef; text-decoration-line: none;\" href=\"https://support.patch.com/hc/en-us/articles/360052941232\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Local Official program</a> on Patch is a better fit for you.&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div class=\"p-rich_text_section\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: #333333; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \'Segoe UI\', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; background-color: #ffffff;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div class=\"p-rich_text_section\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: #333333; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \'Segoe UI\', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; background-color: #ffffff;\">\r\n<div class=\"p-rich_text_section\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span class=\"wysiwyg-font-size-large\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-size: large;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">Hear from Community Organizations on Patch&nbsp;</strong></span></div>\r\n<div class=\"p-rich_text_section\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><em style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">&ldquo;With the demise of many community newspapers, we have found Patch to be a great tool to share information about our free education programs, support groups, upcoming events, etc. with members of our community.&rdquo;</em><br style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\" />&ndash;&nbsp;<strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">Cindy Schelhorn</strong>, Senior Director of Communications &amp; Marketing, Alzheimer&rsquo;s Association National Capital Area Chapter</div>\r\n<div class=\"p-rich_text_section\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div class=\"p-rich_text_section\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><em style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">If you&rsquo;d like to know more about joining Patch or have any other questions, please reach out to us at&nbsp;</em><em style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><a class=\"c-link\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; background-color: transparent; color: #0072ef; text-decoration-line: none;\" href=\"mailto:contributors@patch.com\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">contributors@patch.com</a></em><em style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">.</em></div>\r\n</div>', NULL, '2021-08-18 09:11:03', '2021-08-18 09:11:03'),
(4, 'How can I contribute as a local official on Patch?', 2, '<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: #333333; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \'Segoe UI\', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; background-color: #ffffff;\">Are you a leader in your community?</p>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: #333333; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \'Segoe UI\', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; background-color: #ffffff;\">Do you work to serve your neighbors in a role at a public agency or institution?</p>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: #333333; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \'Segoe UI\', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; background-color: #ffffff;\">If so, you are uniquely qualified to share important news and information with residents. Our platform offers you the opportunity to engage directly with the community you serve at no cost or obligation.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: #333333; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \'Segoe UI\', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; background-color: #ffffff;\"><span class=\"wysiwyg-font-size-large\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-size: large;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">Reach your community</strong></span><br style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\" />Address local concerns and provide critical updates on Patch.</p>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: #333333; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \'Segoe UI\', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; background-color: #ffffff;\"><span class=\"wysiwyg-font-size-large\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-size: large;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">Post where you want</strong></span><br style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\" />Share local information where it is most relevant &ndash; in one or more nearby communities.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: #333333; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \'Segoe UI\', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; background-color: #ffffff;\"><span class=\"wysiwyg-font-size-large\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-size: large;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">Make a local impact</strong></span><br style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\" />With guidance from our editorial staff at your disposal, help your local community stay informed.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: #333333; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \'Segoe UI\', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; background-color: #ffffff;\">Many local officials and agencies just like you are already posting updates and answering questions on Patch. To get started engaging directly with your community:&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: #333333; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \'Segoe UI\', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; background-color: #ffffff;\"><span class=\"wysiwyg-font-size-large\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-size: large;\"><a class=\"c-link\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; background-color: transparent; color: #0072ef; text-decoration-line: none;\" href=\"https://www.patch.com/register\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Create your Patch profile here</a>.</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: #333333; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \'Segoe UI\', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; background-color: #ffffff;\">Once you&rsquo;ve created your profile, please&nbsp;<a class=\"c-link\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; background-color: transparent; color: #0072ef; text-decoration-line: none;\" href=\"https://docs.google.com/forms/d/e/1FAIpQLSdLLz6fRiui0Fwl1eN1CfINzuVXU1TxJbupwxTHcgFH_QtSiQ/viewform\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">fill out this form</a>&nbsp;so we can verify you as a local official.</p>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: #333333; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \'Segoe UI\', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; background-color: #ffffff;\">We look forward to adding you to the fast-growing group of key local leaders engaging with their communities on Patch.</p>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: #333333; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \'Segoe UI\', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; background-color: #ffffff;\"><span class=\"wysiwyg-font-size-large\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-size: large;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">Hear from Local Officials on Patch&nbsp;</strong></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: #333333; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \'Segoe UI\', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; background-color: #ffffff;\"><em style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">&ldquo;Patch makes it very easy for me to share important information with our community.&rdquo;</em><br style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\" />&ndash;&nbsp;<strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">Nicole Ortega</strong>, Student Services, Pacifica School District, Pacifica, California</p>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: #333333; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \'Segoe UI\', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; background-color: #ffffff;\"><em style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">&ldquo;I need notices posted immediately for the public meetings. This is the only place that allows this.&rdquo;</em><br style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\" />&ndash;&nbsp;<strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">Beverly Carle</strong>, Township Clerk, Berkeley Township, New Jersey</p>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: #333333; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \'Segoe UI\', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; background-color: #ffffff;\"><em style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">&ldquo;Patch is a good way to make residents aware of programs available to them.&rdquo;</em><br style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\" />&ndash;&nbsp;<strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">Jeanne Dietsch</strong>, New Hampshire State Senator&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: #333333; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \'Segoe UI\', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; background-color: #ffffff;\"><em style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">&ldquo;I appreciate the ability to target our local area so specifically.&rdquo;</em><br style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\" />&ndash;&nbsp;<strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">Catherine Savage</strong>, Head of Communications, Vernon Area Library, Lincolnshire, Illinois</p>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: #333333; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \'Segoe UI\', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; background-color: #ffffff;\"><em style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">&ldquo;Patch is effective, respected, and has a great reach within our local community.&rdquo;</em><br style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\" />&ndash;&nbsp;<strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">Zachary Mottl</strong>, Village Trustee, Burr Ridge, Illinois</p>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: #333333; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \'Segoe UI\', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; background-color: #ffffff;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: #333333; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \'Segoe UI\', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; background-color: #ffffff;\"><em style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">If you&rsquo;d like to know more about joining Patch or have any other questions, please reach out to us at&nbsp;<a class=\"c-link\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; background-color: transparent; color: #0072ef; text-decoration-line: none;\" href=\"mailto:contributors@patch.com\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">contributors@patch.com</a>.</em></p>', NULL, '2021-08-18 09:16:11', '2021-08-18 09:16:11'),
(5, 'How do I unsubscribe or update my email settings?', 3, '<p><span style=\"color: #333333; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \'Segoe UI\', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; background-color: #ffffff;\">We understand that sometimes we can get a little carried away with emails. To unsubscribe from emails or manage your preferences, click the link at the bottom of every Patch email.&nbsp;</span></p>', NULL, '2021-08-18 09:18:48', '2021-08-18 09:18:48'),
(6, 'What is Patch?', 3, '<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: #333333; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \'Segoe UI\', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; background-color: #ffffff;\">Patch is an independent U.S. local news and information platform. We operate in over a thousand hyperlocal locations in all 50 states and Washington, D.C..&nbsp;We\'re a community-specific news, information and engagement network driven by passionate and experienced media professionals.</p>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: #333333; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \'Segoe UI\', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; background-color: #ffffff;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">Want to get involved?</strong></p>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: #333333; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \'Segoe UI\', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; background-color: #ffffff;\">Here\'s what you can do:</p>\r\n<ul style=\"box-sizing: border-box; list-style-position: outside; list-style-image: initial; margin: 20px 0px 20px 20px; padding: 0px 0px 0px 20px; color: #333333; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \'Segoe UI\', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; background-color: #ffffff;\">\r\n<li style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">Contribute content! Patch welcomes and encourages community members to post directly to the site by signing up&nbsp;<a style=\"box-sizing: border-box; background-color: transparent; color: #0072ef; text-decoration-line: none;\" href=\"https://patch.com/register\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">here.</a></li>\r\n<li style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">Keep up with news and events by subscribing to your local Patch updates</li>\r\n<li style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">Learn more about local businesses and the people behind them</li>\r\n<li style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">Participate in discussions</li>\r\n</ul>', NULL, '2021-08-18 09:1