(4, 'Posting Instructions', 'posting-instructions', '<h1 style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 10px 0px; font-weight: 500; line-height: 1; font-size: 39px; color: #212529; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \'Segoe UI\', Roboto, \'Helvetica Neue\', Arial, \'Noto Sans\', sans-serif, \'Apple Color Emoji\', \'Segoe UI Emoji\', \'Segoe UI Symbol\', \'Noto Color Emoji\'; padding-bottom: 0px; background-color: #ebedef;\">Neighborhood Reporter Posting Instructions</h1>\r\n<h2 class=\"section-heading\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0.5rem; font-weight: 500; line-height: 1.2; font-size: 24px; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \'Segoe UI\', Roboto, \'Helvetica Neue\', Arial, \'Noto Sans\', sans-serif, \'Apple Color Emoji\', \'Segoe UI Emoji\', \'Segoe UI Symbol\', \'Noto Color Emoji\'; color: #333333; padding: 10px 0px; background-color: #ebedef;\">How to reach your neighbors on Neighborhood Reporter</h2>\r\n<h5 style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0.5rem; font-weight: 500; line-height: 1.2; font-size: 15px; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \'Segoe UI\', Roboto, \'Helvetica Neue\', Arial, \'Noto Sans\', sans-serif, \'Apple Color Emoji\', \'Segoe UI Emoji\', \'Segoe UI Symbol\', \'Noto Color Emoji\'; color: #4d4d4d; background-color: #ebedef;\">At Neighborhood Reporter, we believe that local news and information have the power to unite a&nbsp;<span style=\"color: #333333;\">neighborhood </span>. We also believe in giving neighbors the power to tell their own stories and help keep each other informed about what&rsquo;s happening at the local level.</h5>\r\n<h5 style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0.5rem; font-weight: 500; line-height: 1.2; font-size: 15px; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \'Segoe UI\', Roboto, \'Helvetica Neue\', Arial, \'Noto Sans\', sans-serif, \'Apple Color Emoji\', \'Segoe UI Emoji\', \'Segoe UI Symbol\', \'Noto Color Emoji\'; color: #4d4d4d; background-color: #ebedef;\">There are a few different ways to reach out:</h5>\r\n<ul style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 10.5px; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \'Segoe UI\', Roboto, \'Helvetica Neue\', Arial, \'Noto Sans\', sans-serif, \'Apple Color Emoji\', \'Segoe UI Emoji\', \'Segoe UI Symbol\', \'Noto Color Emoji\'; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ebedef; list-style-position: inside; color: #4d4d4d; padding-left: 0px;\">\r\n<li class=\"list-item\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 30px; list-style-position: inside; color: #333333;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: bolder;\">In the&nbsp;<a class=\"page-link\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: #000000; text-decoration-line: none; background-color: transparent; position: relative; display: unset; padding: unset; margin: unset; line-height: normal; border: unset;\" href=\"http://www.neighborhoodreporter.com#neighbor-posts\">Neighborhood Posts</a>&nbsp;section</span>, you can ask a question, share a news tip, recommend something to your neighbors or start a local discussion. (You can also write a more traditional press release, column, letter to the editor or obituary in the form of an&nbsp;<span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: bolder;\"><a class=\"page-link\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: #000000; text-decoration-line: none; background-color: transparent; position: relative; display: unset; padding: unset; margin: unset; line-height: normal; border: unset;\" href=\"http://www.neighborhoodreporter.com#article\">article</a></span>.)</li>\r\n<li class=\"list-item\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 30px; list-style-position: inside; color: #333333;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: bolder;\">On the&nbsp;<a class=\"page-link\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: #000000; text-decoration-line: none; background-color: transparent; position: relative; display: unset; padding: unset; margin: unset; line-height: normal; border: unset;\" href=\"http://www.neighborhoodreporter.com#events\">Events</a>&nbsp;calendar</span>, you can add your own events to the local lineup.</li>\r\n<li class=\"list-item\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 30px; list-style-position: inside; color: #333333;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: bolder;\">In the Marketplace you can place a&nbsp;<a class=\"page-link\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: #000000; text-decoration-line: none; background-color: transparent; position: relative; display: unset; padding: unset; margin: unset; line-height: normal; border: unset;\" href=\"http://www.neighborhoodreporter.com#classifieds\">Classifieds</a> </span>&nbsp;to sell or give away your old stuff; find housing, tenants or roommates; find job candidates or offer your services; and make other local business announcements.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h5 style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0.5rem; font-weight: 500; line-height: 1.2; font-size: 15px; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \'Segoe UI\', Roboto, \'Helvetica Neue\', Arial, \'Noto Sans\', sans-serif, \'Apple Color Emoji\', \'Segoe UI Emoji\', \'Segoe UI Symbol\', \'Noto Color Emoji\'; color: #4d4d4d; background-color: #ebedef;\"><a style=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: #007bff; text-decoration-line: none; background-color: transparent;\" href=\"http://www.neighborhoodreporter.com/register\">Log in</a>&nbsp;or&nbsp;<a style=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: #007bff; text-decoration-line: none; background-color: transparent;\" href=\"http://www.neighborhoodreporter.com/register\">sign up</a>&nbsp;to start posting. Or find out more about Neighborhood Reporter&rsquo;s various posting types below.</h5>\r\n<h2 class=\"section-heading\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0.5rem; font-weight: 500; line-height: 1.2; font-size: 24px; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \'Segoe UI\', Roboto, \'Helvetica Neue\', Arial, \'Noto Sans\', sans-serif, \'Apple Color Emoji\', \'Segoe UI Emoji\', \'Segoe UI Symbol\', \'Noto Color Emoji\'; color: #333333; padding: 10px 0px; background-color: #ebedef;\">What to post where</h2>\r\n<h3 class=\"sub-heading\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0.5rem; font-weight: 500; line-height: 1.2; font-size: 18px; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \'Segoe UI\', Roboto, \'Helvetica Neue\', Arial, \'Noto Sans\', sans-serif, \'Apple Color Emoji\', \'Segoe UI Emoji\', \'Segoe UI Symbol\', \'Noto Color Emoji\'; color: #333333; padding: 10px 0px; background-color: #ebedef;\"><a class=\"section-link\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: #007bff; background-color: transparent;\" name=\"neighbor-posts\"></a>Neighbor Posts</h3>\r\n<h5 style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0.5rem; font-weight: 500; line-height: 1.2; font-size: 15px; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \'Segoe UI\', Roboto, \'Helvetica Neue\', Arial, \'Noto Sans\', sans-serif, \'Apple Color Emoji\', \'Segoe UI Emoji\', \'Segoe UI Symbol\', \'Noto Color Emoji\'; color: #4d4d4d; background-color: #ebedef;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: bolder;\">You want to post a:</span></h5>\r\n<ul class=\"mt-0\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 10.5px; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \'Segoe UI\', Roboto, \'Helvetica Neue\', Arial, \'Noto Sans\', sans-serif, \'Apple Color Emoji\', \'Segoe UI Emoji\', \'Segoe UI Symbol\', \'Noto Color Emoji\'; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ebedef; list-style-position: inside; color: #4d4d4d; padding-left: 0px;\">\r\n<li class=\"mb-0 list-item\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 30px; list-style-position: inside; color: #333333;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: bolder;\">Question</span>&nbsp;about your community</li>\r\n<li class=\"mb-0 list-item\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 30px; list-style-position: inside; color: #333333;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: bolder;\">News tip</span>&nbsp;about something going on in the neighborhood</li>\r\n<li class=\"mb-0 list-item\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 30px; list-style-position: inside; color: #333333;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: bolder;\">Recommendation</span>&nbsp;for a local business or service</li>\r\n<li class=\"mb-0 list-item\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 30px; list-style-position: inside; color: #333333;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: bolder;\">Opinion</span>&nbsp;about a local issue</li>\r\n<li class=\"mb-0 list-item\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 30px; list-style-position: inside; color: #333333;\">Photo you took in town</li>\r\n<li class=\"mb-0 list-item\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 30px; list-style-position: inside; color: #333333;\">Other quick local updates</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h4 class=\"pt-2 pb-3\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; font-weight: 500; line-height: 1.2; font-size: 18px; color: #212529; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \'Segoe UI\', Roboto, \'Helvetica Neue\', Arial, \'Noto Sans\', sans-serif, \'Apple Color Emoji\', \'Segoe UI Emoji\', \'Segoe UI Symbol\', \'Noto Color Emoji\'; background-color: #ebedef; padding-top: 0.5rem !important; padding-bottom: 1rem !important;\"><a style=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: #007bff; text-decoration-line: none; background-color: transparent;\" href=\"http://patch.com/compose\">Post a Neighbor Post</a></h4>\r\n<h5 style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0.5rem; font-weight: 500; line-height: 1.2; font-size: 15px; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \'Segoe UI\', Roboto, \'Helvetica Neue\', Arial, \'Noto Sans\', sans-serif, \'Apple Color Emoji\', \'Segoe UI Emoji\', \'Segoe UI Symbol\', \'Noto Color Emoji\'; color: #4d4d4d; background-color: #ebedef;\">The Neighbor Posts section is a community forum and social platform designed to connect you to other neighbors &mdash; as well as Neighborhood Reporter reporters, local officials, nonprofits, businesses and experts in your area.</h5>\r\n<h5 style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0.5rem; font-weight: 500; line-height: 1.2; font-size: 15px; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \'Segoe UI\', Roboto, \'Helvetica Neue\', Arial, \'Noto Sans\', sans-serif, \'Apple Color Emoji\', \'Segoe UI Emoji\', \'Segoe UI Symbol\', \'Noto Color Emoji\'; color: #4d4d4d; background-color: #ebedef;\">When you&nbsp;<a style=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: #007bff; text-decoration-line: none; background-color: transparent;\" href=\"../../../register\">post in this section</a>, your post will appear at the top of the Neighbor Posts page. If it receives enough attention and engagement, it may likewise appear on the homepage for your community or in an email sent to local readers.</h5>\r\n<h5 style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0.5rem; font-weight: 500; line-height: 1.2; font-size: 15px; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \'Segoe UI\', Roboto, \'Helvetica Neue\', Arial, \'Noto Sans\', sans-serif, \'Apple Color Emoji\', \'Segoe UI Emoji\', \'Segoe UI Symbol\', \'Noto Color Emoji\'; color: #4d4d4d; background-color: #ebedef;\">You can also reply to any other posts you see on Neighborhood Reporter, to help answer your neighbors&rsquo; questions and participate in local discussions. We encourage neighbors to come together to help each other understand their community better &mdash; because Neighborhood Reporter reporters can&rsquo;t catch everything, and it takes a village to keep track of what&rsquo;s happening on the ground.</h5>\r\n<h5 style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0.5rem; font-weight: 500; line-height: 1.2; font-size: 15px; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \'Segoe UI\', Roboto, \'Helvetica Neue\', Arial, \'Noto Sans\', sans-serif, \'Apple Color Emoji\', \'Segoe UI Emoji\', \'Segoe UI Symbol\', \'Noto Color Emoji\'; color: #4d4d4d; background-color: #ebedef;\">Always remember to keep your posts and replies local, clean, friendly and factual, in keeping with the&nbsp;<a style=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: #007bff; text-decoration-line: none; background-color: transparent;\" href=\"http://www.neighborhoodreporter.com/community-guidelines\">Neighborhood Reporter Community Guidelines</a>. And to make Neighborhood Reporter a better place for neighbors, please flag any other posts or replies that don\'t follow these rules.</h5>\r\n<h5 style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0.5rem; font-weight: 500; line-height: 1.2; font-size: 15px; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \'Segoe UI\', Roboto, \'Helvetica Neue\', Arial, \'Noto Sans\', sans-serif, \'Apple Color Emoji\', \'Segoe UI Emoji\', \'Segoe UI Symbol\', \'Noto Color Emoji\'; color: #4d4d4d; background-color: #ebedef;\">(Are you a local official? Make sure to&nbsp;<a style=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: #007bff; text-decoration-line: none; background-color: transparent;\" href=\"#\">apply for a local official badge</a>, so the community knows to trust your posts and replies.)</h5>\r\n<h3 class=\"sub-heading\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0.5rem; font-weight: 500; line-height: 1.2; font-size: 18px; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \'Segoe UI\', Roboto, \'Helvetica Neue\', Arial, \'Noto Sans\', sans-serif, \'Apple Color Emoji\', \'Segoe UI Emoji\', \'Segoe UI Symbol\', \'Noto Color Emoji\'; color: #333333; padding: 10px 0px; background-color: #ebedef;\"><a class=\"section-link\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: #007bff; background-color: transparent;\" name=\"article\"></a>Articles</h3>\r\n<h5 style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0.5rem; font-weight: 500; line-height: 1.2; font-size: 15px; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \'Segoe UI\', Roboto, \'Helvetica Neue\', Arial, \'Noto Sans\', sans-serif, \'Apple Color Emoji\', \'Segoe UI Emoji\', \'Segoe UI Symbol\', \'Noto Color Emoji\'; color: #4d4d4d; background-color: #ebedef;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: bolder;\">You want to post a:</span></h5>\r\n<ul class=\"mt-0\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 10.5px; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \'Segoe UI\', Roboto, \'Helvetica Neue\', Arial, \'Noto Sans\', sans-serif, \'Apple Color Emoji\', \'Segoe UI Emoji\', \'Segoe UI Symbol\', \'Noto Color Emoji\'; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ebedef; list-style-position: inside; color: #4d4d4d; padding-left: 0px;\">\r\n<li class=\"mb-0 list-item\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 30px; list-style-position: inside; color: #333333;\">Press release</li>\r\n<li class=\"mb-0 list-item\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 30px; list-style-position: inside; color: #333333;\">Column or op-ed</li>\r\n<li class=\"mb-0 list-item\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 30px; list-style-position: inside; color: #333333;\">Letter to the editor</li>\r\n<li class=\"mb-0 list-item\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 30px; list-style-position: inside; color: #333333;\">Obituary</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h4 class=\"pt-2 pb-3\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; font-weight: 500; line-height: 1.2; font-size: 18px; color: #212529; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \'Segoe UI\', Roboto, \'Helvetica Neue\', Arial, \'Noto Sans\', sans-serif, \'Apple Color Emoji\', \'Segoe UI Emoji\', \'Segoe UI Symbol\', \'Noto Color Emoji\'; background-color: #ebedef; padding-top: 0.5rem !important; padding-bottom: 1rem !important;\"><a style=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: #007bff; text-decoration-line: none; background-color: transparent;\" href=\"https://my.patch.com/node/add/article\">Post an Article</a></h4>\r\n<h5 style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0.5rem; font-weight: 500; line-height: 1.2; font-size: 15px; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \'Segoe UI\', Roboto, \'Helvetica Neue\', Arial, \'Noto Sans\', sans-serif, \'Apple Color Emoji\', \'Segoe UI Emoji\', \'Segoe UI Symbol\', \'Noto Color Emoji\'; color: #4d4d4d; background-color: #ebedef;\">If you&rsquo;re looking to contribute in a more formal or traditional way, you have the option to complete one additional verification step in order to post a press release, column, op-ed, letter to the editor or obituary in the form of an&nbsp;<a style=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: #007bff; text-decoration-line: none; background-color: transparent;\" href=\"../../../register?ru=https://www.neighborhoodreporter.com/add/article\">article</a>.</h5>\r\n<h5 style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0.5rem; font-weight: 500; line-height: 1.2; font-size: 15px; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \'Segoe UI\', Roboto, \'Helvetica Neue\', Arial, \'Noto Sans\', sans-serif, \'Apple Color Emoji\', \'Segoe UI Emoji\', \'Segoe UI Symbol\', \'Noto Color Emoji\'; color: #4d4d4d; background-color: #ebedef;\">When you publish an article on Neighborhood Reporter, it will be labeled as &ldquo;Neighborhood News&rdquo; and will show up in the Neighborhood Posts section of your home community. If your local Neighborhood Reporter editor sees fit, they can also choose to share it with nearby communities or include it in an email to readers.</h5>\r\n<h5 style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0.5rem; font-weight: 500; line-height: 1.2; font-size: 15px; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \'Segoe UI\', Roboto, \'Helvetica Neue\', Arial, \'Noto Sans\', sans-serif, \'Apple Color Emoji\', \'Segoe UI Emoji\', \'Segoe UI Symbol\', \'Noto Color Emoji\'; color: #4d4d4d; background-color: #ebedef;\">Neighborhood Reporter also welcomes vetted contributors interested in sharing their expertise and reporting on their communities more deeply. To apply, email&nbsp;<a style=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: #007bff; text-decoration-line: none; background-color: transparent;\" href=\"mailto:contributors@patch.com\">contributors@neighborhoodreporter.com</a>&nbsp;with a link to your Neighborhood Reporter profile, some examples of your work and a few sentences on why you&rsquo;d like to contribute.</h5>\r\n<h3 class=\"sub-heading\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0.5rem; font-weight: 500; line-height: 1.2; font-size: 18px; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \'Segoe UI\', Roboto, \'Helvetica Neue\', Arial, \'Noto Sans\', sans-serif, \'Apple Color Emoji\', \'Segoe UI Emoji\', \'Segoe UI Symbol\', \'Noto Color Emoji\'; color: #333333; padding: 10px 0px; background-color: #ebedef;\"><a class=\"section-link\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: #007bff; background-color: transparent;\" name=\"events\"></a>Events</h3>\r\n<h5 style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0.5rem; font-weight: 500; line-height: 1.2; font-size: 15px; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \'Segoe UI\', Roboto, \'Helvetica Neue\', Arial, \'Noto Sans\', sans-serif, \'Apple Color Emoji\', \'Segoe UI Emoji\', \'Segoe UI Symbol\', \'Noto Color Emoji\'; color: #4d4d4d; background-color: #ebedef;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: bolder;\">You want to post a:</span></h5>\r\n<ul class=\"mt-0\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 10.5px; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \'Segoe UI\', Roboto, \'Helvetica Neue\', Arial, \'Noto Sans\', sans-serif, \'Apple Color Emoji\', \'Segoe UI Emoji\', \'Segoe UI Symbol\', \'Noto Color Emoji\'; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ebedef; list-style-position: inside; color: #4d4d4d; padding-left: 0px;\">\r\n<li class=\"mb-0 list-item\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 30px; list-style-position: inside; color: #333333;\">Fundraiser</li>\r\n<li class=\"mb-0 list-item\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 30px; list-style-position: inside; color: #333333;\">Yard sale</li>\r\n<li class=\"mb-0 list-item\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 30px; list-style-position: inside; color: #333333;\">Open house</li>\r\n<li class=\"mb-0 list-item\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 30px; list-style-position: inside; color: #333333;\">Festival or parade</li>\r\n<li class=\"mb-0 list-item\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 30px; list-style-position: inside; color: #333333;\">Other local activities</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h4 class=\"pt-2 pb-3\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; font-weight: 500; line-height: 1.2; font-size: 18px; color: #212529; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \'Segoe UI\', Roboto, \'Helvetica Neue\', Arial, \'Noto Sans\', sans-serif, \'Apple Color Emoji\', \'Segoe UI Emoji\', \'Segoe UI Symbol\', \'Noto Color Emoji\'; background-color: #ebedef; padding-top: 0.5rem !important; padding-bottom: 1rem !important;\"><a style=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: #007bff; text-decoration-line: none; background-color: transparent;\" href=\"../../../register\">Post an Event</a></h4>\r\n<h5 style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0.5rem; font-weight: 500; line-height: 1.2; font-size: 15px; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \'Segoe UI\', Roboto, \'Helvetica Neue\', Arial, \'Noto Sans\', sans-serif, \'Apple Color Emoji\', \'Segoe UI Emoji\', \'Segoe UI Symbol\', \'Noto Color Emoji\'; color: #4d4d4d; background-color: #ebedef;\">Adding your event to the Neighborhood Reporter neighborhood Calendar is a great way to boost attendance and let neighbors know about fun stuff happening near them. If the thing you&rsquo;re posting about has a date and time, it should always be <a style=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: #007bff; text-decoration-line: none; background-color: transparent;\" href=\"../../../register\">posted as an event</a><span style=\"font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \'Segoe UI\', Roboto, \'Helvetica Neue\', Arial, \'Noto Sans\', sans-serif, \'Apple Color Emoji\', \'Segoe UI Emoji\', \'Segoe UI Symbol\', \'Noto Color Emoji\';\">.</span></h5>\r\n<h5 style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0.5rem; font-weight: 500; line-height: 1.2; font-size: 15px; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \'Segoe UI\', Roboto, \'Helvetica Neue\', Arial, \'Noto Sans\', sans-serif, \'Apple Color Emoji\', \'Segoe UI Emoji\', \'Segoe UI Symbol\', \'Noto Color Emoji\'; color: #4d4d4d; background-color: #ebedef;\">Once posted, your event will appear in the main Calendar section for your neighborhood, and sometimes in other event preview sections across Neighborhood Reporter and in emails to readers.</h5>\r\n<h5 style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0.5rem; font-weight: 500; line-height: 1.2; font-size: 15px; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \'Segoe UI\', Roboto, \'Helvetica Neue\', Arial, \'Noto Sans\', sans-serif, \'Apple Color Emoji\', \'Segoe UI Emoji\', \'Segoe UI Symbol\', \'Noto Color Emoji\'; color: #4d4d4d; background-color: #ebedef;\">To boost your listing and give it extra visibility, you can also pay to promote it as &ldquo;Featured&rdquo; across the region for $1 per day per neighborhood.&nbsp;</h5>\r\n<h3 class=\"sub-heading\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0.5rem; font-weight: 500; line-height: 1.2; font-size: 18px; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \'Segoe UI\', Roboto, \'Helvetica Neue\', Arial, \'Noto Sans\', sans-serif, \'Apple Color Emoji\', \'Segoe UI Emoji\', \'Segoe UI Symbol\', \'Noto Color Emoji\'; color: #333333; padding: 10px 0px; background-color: #ebedef;\"><a class=\"section-link\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: #007bff; background-color: transparent;\" name=\"classifieds\"></a>Classifieds</h3>\r\n<h5 style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0.5rem; font-weight: 500; line-height: 1.2; font-size: 15px; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \'Segoe UI\', Roboto, \'Helvetica Neue\', Arial, \'Noto Sans\', sans-serif, \'Apple Color Emoji\', \'Segoe UI Emoji\', \'Segoe UI Symbol\', \'Noto Color Emoji\'; color: #4d4d4d; background-color: #ebedef;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: bolder;\">You want to post about:</span></h5>\r\n<ul class=\"mt-0\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 10.5px; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \'Segoe UI\', Roboto, \'Helvetica Neue\', Arial, \'Noto Sans\', sans-serif, \'Apple Color Emoji\', \'Segoe UI Emoji\', \'Segoe UI Symbol\', \'Noto Color Emoji\'; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ebedef; list-style-position: inside; color: #4d4d4d; padding-left: 0px;\">\r\n<li class=\"mb-0 list-item\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 30px; list-style-position: inside; color: #333333;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: bolder;\">Lost &amp; found</span>&nbsp;pets or other items</li>\r\n<li class=\"mb-0 list-item\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 30px; list-style-position: inside; color: #333333;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: bolder;\">Housing</span>&nbsp;(seeking or offering)</li>\r\n<li class=\"mb-0 list-item\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 30px; list-style-position: inside; color: #333333;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: bolder;\">Gigs &amp; services</span>&nbsp;(seeking or offering)</li>\r\n<li class=\"mb-0 list-item\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 30px; list-style-position: inside; color: #333333;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: bolder;\">For sale</span>&nbsp;items</li>\r\n<li class=\"mb-0 list-item\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 30px; list-style-position: inside; color: #333333;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: bolder;\">Free stuff</span>&nbsp;you want to get rid of</li>\r\n<li class=\"mb-0 list-item\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 30px; list-style-position: inside; color: #333333;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: bolder;\">Announcement</span>&nbsp;about your business or org</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h4 class=\"pt-2 pb-3\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; font-weight: 500; line-height: 1.2; font-size: 18px; color: #212529; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \'Segoe UI\', Roboto, \'Helvetica Neue\', Arial, \'Noto Sans\', sans-serif, \'Apple Color Emoji\', \'Segoe UI Emoji\', \'Segoe UI Symbol\', \'Noto Color Emoji\'; background-color: #ebedef; padding-top: 0.5rem !important; padding-bottom: 1rem !important;\"><a style=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: #007bff; text-decoration-line: none; background-color: transparent;\" href=\"http://patch.com/compose/classified\">Post a Classified</a></h4>\r\n<h5 style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0.5rem; font-weight: 500; line-height: 1.2; font-size: 15px; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \'Segoe UI\', Roboto, \'Helvetica Neue\', Arial, \'Noto Sans\', sans-serif, \'Apple Color Emoji\', \'Segoe UI Emoji\', \'Segoe UI Symbol\', \'Noto Color Emoji\'; color: #4d4d4d; background-color: #ebedef;\">The Classifieds section serves as a local marketplace where you can sell or give away your stuff, look for work, find roommates or tenants and make other local business announcements.</h5>\r\n<h5 style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0.5rem; font-weight: 500; line-height: 1.2; font-size: 15px; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \'Segoe UI\', Roboto, \'Helvetica Neue\', Arial, \'Noto Sans\', sans-serif, \'Apple Color Emoji\', \'Segoe UI Emoji\', \'Segoe UI Symbol\', \'Noto Color Emoji\'; color: #4d4d4d; background-color: #ebedef;\">Once posted, your classified will appear in the main Classifieds section for your neighborhood, and sometimes in other preview sections across Neighborhood Reporter and in emails to readers. Interested parties can use a contact form that will appear inside your post to email you directly about your offer.</h5>\r\n<h5 style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0.5rem; font-weight: 500; line-height: 1.2; font-size: 15px; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \'Segoe UI\', Roboto, \'Helvetica Neue\', Arial, \'Noto Sans\', sans-serif, \'Apple Color Emoji\', \'Segoe UI Emoji\', \'Segoe UI Symbol\', \'Noto Color Emoji\'; color: #4d4d4d; background-color: #ebedef;\">To boost your listing and give it extra visibility, you can also pay to promote it as &ldquo;featured&rdquo; across the region for $1 per day per community.</h5>\r\n<hr style=\"box-sizing: content-box; height: 0px; overflow: visible; margin-top: 20px; margin-bottom: 20px; border: unset; color: #212529; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \'Segoe UI\', Roboto, \'Helvetica Neue\', Arial, \'Noto Sans\', sans-serif, \'Apple Color Emoji\', \'Segoe UI Emoji\', \'Segoe UI Symbol\', \'Noto Color Emoji\'; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ebedef; display: inline-block;\" />\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h5 style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0.5rem; font-weight: 500; line-height: 1.2; font-size: 15px; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \'Segoe UI\', Roboto, \'Helvetica Neue\', Arial, \'Noto Sans\', sans-serif, \'Apple Color Emoji\', \'Segoe UI Emoji\', \'Segoe UI Symbol\', \'Noto Color Emoji\'; color: #4d4d4d; background-color: #ebedef;\">Still have questions about posting on Neighborhood Reporter? Read more in&nbsp;<a style=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: #007bff; text-decoration-line: none; background-color: transparent;\" href=\"http://www.neighborhoodreporter.com/faqCategory\">our FAQ section</a>, or contact our support team anytime at&nbsp;<a style=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: #007bff; text-decoration-line: none; background-color: transparent;\" href=\"mailto:support@patch.com\">support@neighborhoodreporter.com</a>.</h5>', NULL, NULL, '2021-10-01 20:28:30');
