4d4d; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \'Segoe UI\', Roboto, \'Helvetica Neue\', Arial, \'Noto Sans\', sans-serif, \'Apple Color Emoji\', \'Segoe UI Emoji\', \'Segoe UI Symbol\', \'Noto Color Emoji\'; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ebedef;\">\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 1rem; font-size: 14px;\">If you have any questions or comments about our Terms of Use or anything else, you may contact us at:<br style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\" />Planck, LLC, d/b/a Neighborhood Reporter Media<br style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\" /><br style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\" />Email:&nbsp;<a style=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: #007bff; text-decoration-line: none; background-color: transparent;\" href=\"mailto:support@neighborhoodreporter.com\">support@neighborhoodreporter.com</a></p>\r\n</section>', NULL, NULL, '2021-10-01 20:43:23');
