on to your Personal Information under applicable European data privacy laws under the General Data Protection Regulation and other applicable data protection laws, which may be amended from time to time (&ldquo;European Data Privacy Laws&rdquo;). This section only applies to such users. Under applicable European Data Privacy Laws, Neighborhood Reporter is the data controller.</p>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 12px 0px; color: #212529; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \'Segoe UI\', Roboto, \'Helvetica Neue\', Arial, \'Noto Sans\', sans-serif, \'Apple Color Emoji\', \'Segoe UI Emoji\', \'Segoe UI Symbol\', \'Noto Color Emoji\'; background-color: #ebedef; font-size: 14px; line-height: normal;\">We collect Personal Information when you access our website, public registers, social media, publicly accessible websites, or if you access or use the Service on a mobile device. Please see the main Privacy Policy for further information on &ldquo;Personal Information We Collect&rdquo;.</p>\r\n<h3 style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0.5rem; font-weight: 500; line-height: 1.2; font-size: 16px; color: #212529; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \'Segoe UI\', Roboto, \'Helvetica Neue\', Arial, \'Noto Sans\', sans-serif, \'Apple Color Emoji\', \'Segoe UI Emoji\', \'Segoe UI Symbol\', \'Noto Color Emoji\'; background-color: #ebedef;\">Rights to Control Personal information</h3>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 12px 0px; color: #212529; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \'Segoe UI\', Roboto, \'Helvetica Neue\', Arial, \'Noto Sans\', sans-serif, \'Apple Color Emoji\', \'Segoe UI Emoji\', \'Segoe UI Symbol\', \'Noto Color Emoji\'; background-color: #ebedef; font-size: 14px; line-height: normal;\">Under the applicable European Data Privacy Laws, you have the right to ensure your Personal Information is accurate. You have the right to request that we correct any inaccurate Personal Information. You also have the right to request that we delete or restrict the processing of your Personal Information, although we are permitted to retain it where we still have an ongoing purpose to retain it or as otherwise permitted under the European Data Privacy Laws. This may compromise our ability to provide you with our Services. You also have the right to transfer your Personal Information to another service provider subject to the European Data Privacy Laws. We will, following your written request to us, provide you with your relevant Personal Information in a machine-readable format to transfer to another service provider. We will aim to respond to your request within one calendar month of receipt of the request. Where we are unable to do so within the calendar month, we will notify you of our need to extend this timeline. There are certain exemptions and restrictions applicable to the exercise of these rights under the European Data Privacy Laws that enable Personal Information to be retained, processed or withheld from access and we will inform you of these, if applicable. To make any of these requests or to opt out of receiving marketing communications, please contact us at&nbsp;<a style=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: #007bff; text-decoration-line: none; background-color: transparent;\" href=\"mailto:privacy@neighborhoodreporter.com\">privacy@neighborhoodreporter.com</a>.</p>\r\n<h3 style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0.5rem; font-weight: 500; line-height: 1.2; font-size: 16px; color: #212529; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \'Segoe UI\', Roboto, \'Helvetica Neue\', Arial, \'Noto Sans\', sans-serif, \'Apple Color Emoji\', \'Segoe UI Emoji\', \'Segoe UI Symbol\', \'Noto Color Emoji\'; background-color: #ebedef;\">International Transfers</h3>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 12px 0px; color: #212529; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \'Segoe UI\', Roboto, \'Helvetica Neue\', Arial, \'Noto Sans\', sans-serif, \'Apple Color Emoji\', \'Segoe UI Emoji\', \'Segoe UI Symbol\', \'Noto Color Emoji\'; background-color: #ebedef; font-size: 14px; line-height: normal;\">If you are in the EU/EEA/UK, you will be visiting Neighborhood Reporter from a location outside of the United States and therefore you will be connected through and to servers located within the United States (where data privacy laws are less stringent than in the EU/EEA/UK and some other jurisdictions). Some of the recipients processing your Personal Information may be located in countries (including the United States) that do not provide a level of data protection equivalent to that set forth by the EEA and some other jurisdictions. Neighborhood Reporter will take appropriate steps to ensure that such recipients act in accordance with the European Data Privacy Laws.</p>\r\n<h3 style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0.5rem; font-weight: 500; line-height: 1.2; font-size: 16px; color: #212529; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \'Segoe UI\', Roboto, \'Helvetica Neue\', Arial, \'Noto Sans\', sans-serif, \'Apple Color Emoji\', \'Segoe UI Emoji\', \'Segoe UI Symbol\', \'Noto Color Emoji\'; background-color: #ebedef;\">Sharing your Personal information</h3>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 12px 0px; color: #212529; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \'Segoe UI\', Roboto, \'Helvetica Neue\', Arial, \'Noto Sans\', sans-serif, \'Apple Color Emoji\', \'Segoe UI Emoji\', \'Segoe UI Symbol\', \'Noto Color Emoji\'; background-color: #ebedef; font-size: 14px; line-height: normal;\">We share your Personal Information with OneTrust, LLC (&ldquo;OneTrust&rdquo;), a service provider for our website platform and associated technology. By using our Services, you are giving us your consent for us to share your Personal Information with OneTrust. OneTrust will process your Personal Information in compliance with Standard Contractual Clauses approved by the European Commission, which shall provide the same level of protection to your Personal Information required to fulfill their legal obligations under the Data Privacy Laws. We do not allow our third-party service providers to use your Personal Information for their own purposes and only permit them to process your Personal Information for specified purposes and in accordance with our instructions.</p>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 12px 0px; color: #212529; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \'Segoe UI\', Roboto, \'Helvetica Neue\', Arial, \'Noto Sans\', sans-serif, \'Apple Color Emoji\', \'Segoe UI Emoji\', \'Segoe UI Symbol\', \'Noto Color Emoji\'; background-color: #ebedef; font-size: 14px; line-height: normal;\">Please see the section &ldquo;How We Disclose Your Information&rdquo; in the main Privacy Policy for further information on how we share your Personal Information with other third parties.</p>\r\n<h3 style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0.5rem; font-weight: 500; line-height: 1.2; font-size: 16px; color: #212529; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \'Segoe UI\', Roboto, \'Helvetica Neue\', Arial, \'Noto Sans\', sans-serif, \'Apple Color Emoji\', \'Segoe UI Emoji\', \'Segoe UI Symbol\', \'Noto Color Emoji\'; background-color: #ebedef;\">Tracking Tools (&ldquo;Cookies&rdquo;)</h3>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 12px 0px; color: #212529; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \'Segoe UI\', Roboto, \'Helvetica Neue\', Arial, \'Noto Sans\', sans-serif, \'Apple Color Emoji\', \'Segoe UI Emoji\', \'Segoe UI Symbol\', \'Noto Color Emoji\'; background-color: #ebedef; font-size: 14px; line-height: normal;\">Please see the section &ldquo;Cookies, Web Beacons and Similar Technologies&rdquo; in the main Privacy Policy for information on how we use cookies. Please note, if you choose to block or delete cookies, certain features of our Site may not operate correctly. For more information, see&nbsp;<a style=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: #007bff; text-decoration-line: none; background-color: transparent;\" href=\"http://www.allaboutcookies.org/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\">www.allaboutcookies.org</a>.</p>\r\n<h3 style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0.5rem; font-weight: 500; line-height: 1.2; font-size: 16px; color: #212529; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \'Segoe UI\', Roboto, \'Helvetica Neue\', Arial, \'Noto Sans\', sans-serif, \'Apple Color Emoji\', \'Segoe UI Emoji\', \'Segoe UI Symbol\', \'Noto Color Emoji\'; background-color: #ebedef;\">Protection of Children</h3>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 12px 0px; color: #212529; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \'Segoe UI\', Roboto, \'Helvetica Neue\', Arial, \'Noto Sans\', sans-serif, \'Apple Color Emoji\', \'Segoe UI Emoji\', \'Segoe UI Symbol\', \'Noto Color Emoji\'; background-color: #ebedef; font-size: 14px; line-height: normal;\">Under applicable European Data Privacy Laws, children between the age of 13 to 16 may provide valid consent to process their Personal Information. Where consent is required under such European Data Privacy Laws, you have an obligation to provide to us evidence of such consent or, as required under the European Data Privacy Laws, the authorization of the holder of parental responsibility for the child. We may refuse to process, or continue to process, the child&rsquo;s Personal Information until we receive this evidence of consent or authorization. If we become aware that Personal Information has been collected from a child under age 13 (or such higher age as required by applicable law), we will take steps to delete that information as soon as possible.</p>\r\n<h3 style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0.5rem; font-weight: 500; line-height: 1.2; font-size: 16px; color: #212529; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \'Segoe UI\', Roboto, \'Helvetica Neue\', Arial, \'Noto Sans\', sans-serif, \'Apple Color Emoji\', \'Segoe UI Emoji\', \'Segoe UI Symbol\', \'Noto Color Emoji\'; background-color: #ebedef;\">Retention of Personal information</h3>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 12px 0px; color: #212529; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \'Segoe UI\', Roboto, \'Helvetica Neue\', Arial, \'Noto Sans\', sans-serif, \'Apple Color Emoji\', \'Segoe UI Emoji\', \'Segoe UI Symbol\', \'Noto Color Emoji\'; background-color: #ebedef; font-size: 14px; line-height: normal;\">We will only retain your Personal Information for as long as reasonably necessary to fulfill the purposes we collected it for, including for the purposes of satisfying any legal requirements. To determine the appropriate retention period, we consider the amount, nature and sensitivity of the Personal Information, the potential risk of harm from unauthorized use or disclosure of your Personal information, the purposes for which we process your Personal Information and whether we can achieve those purposes through other means, and applicable legal requirements.</p>\r\n<h3 style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0.5rem; font-weight: 500; line-height: 1.2; font-size: 16px; color: #212529; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \'Segoe UI\', Roboto, \'Helvetica Neue\', Arial, \'Noto Sans\', sans-serif, \'Apple Color Emoji\', \'Segoe UI Emoji\', \'Segoe UI Symbol\', \'Noto Color Emoji\'; background-color: #ebedef;\">Data security</h3>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 12px 0px; color: #212529; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \'Segoe UI\', Roboto, \'Helvetica Neue\', Arial, \'Noto Sans\', sans-serif, \'Apple Color Emoji\', \'Segoe UI Emoji\', \'Segoe UI Symbol\', \'Noto Color Emoji\'; background-color: #ebedef; font-size: 14px; line-height: normal;\">We have put in place appropriate security measures to prevent your Personal Information from being accidentally lost, used or accessed in an unauthorised way, altered or disclosed. In addition, we limit access to your Personal Information to those employees, agents, contractors and other third parties who have a business need to know. They will only process your Personal Information on our instructions, and they are subject to a duty of confidentiality.</p>\r\n<h3 style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0.5rem; font-weight: 500; line-height: 1.2; font-size: 16px; color: #212529; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \'Segoe UI\', Roboto, \'Helvetica Neue\', Arial, \'Noto Sans\', sans-serif, \'Apple Color Emoji\', \'Segoe UI Emoji\', \'Segoe UI Symbol\', \'Noto Color Emoji\'; background-color: #ebedef;\">Complaint Process</h3>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 12px 0px; color: #212529; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \'Segoe UI\', Roboto, \'Helvetica Neue\', Arial, \'Noto Sans\', sans-serif, \'Apple Color Emoji\', \'Segoe UI Emoji\', \'Segoe UI Symbol\', \'Noto Color Emoji\'; background-color: #ebedef; font-size: 14px; line-height: normal;\">If you have any concerns regarding how we are handling your Personal Information, please contact us. We will endeavour to deal with your concerns promptly. If you wish to complain about the handling of your Personal Information outside of Neighborhood Reporter, you have the right to raise a complaint with a supervisory authority in your country of residence if applicable under European Data Privacy Laws.</p>\r\n<h2 id=\"annex-2\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 12px; font-weight: 500; line-height: 1.2; font-size: 21px; color: #212529; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \'Segoe UI\', Roboto, \'Helvetica Neue\', Arial, \'Noto Sans\', sans-serif, \'Apple Color Emoji\', \'Segoe UI Emoji\', \'Segoe UI Symbol\', \'Noto Color Emoji\'; text-align: center; background-color: #ebedef;\">Annex 2<br style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\" />California Consumer Privacy Act Disclosures</h2>\r\n<h3 style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0.5rem; font-weight: 500; line-height: 1.2; font-size: 16px; color: #212529; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \'Segoe UI\', Roboto, \'Helvetica Neue\', Arial, \'Noto Sans\', sans-serif, \'Apple Color Emoji\', \'Segoe UI Emoji\', \'Segoe UI Symbol\', \'Noto Color Emoji\'; background-color: #ebedef;\">Effective Date: January 1, 2020</h3>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 12px 0px; color: #212529; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \'Segoe UI\', Roboto, \'Helvetica Neue\', Arial, \'Noto Sans\', sans-serif, \'Apple Color Emoji\', \'Segoe UI Emoji\', \'Segoe UI Symbol\', \'Noto Color Emoji\'; background-color: #ebedef; font-size: 14px; line-height: normal;\">These California Consumer Privacy Act Disclosures (&ldquo;California Disclosures&rdquo;) include disclosures required under the California Consumer Privacy Act (&ldquo;CCPA&rdquo;), and supplement the Neighborhood Reporter&nbsp;<a style=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: #007bff; text-decoration-line: none; background-color: transparent;\" href=\"http://www.neighborhoodreporter.com/privacy\">Privacy Policy</a>. Please see the Neighborhood Reporter Privacy Policy for more information regarding how Neighborhood Reporter collects, uses, discloses and safeguards your Personal Information. Capitalized terms not otherwise defined in these California Disclosures have the meanings set forth in the&nbsp;<a style=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: #007bff; text-decoration-line: none; background-color: transparent;\" href=\"http://projects.discussion4all.com/privacy\">Privacy Policy</a>.</p>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 12px 0px; color: #212529; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \'Segoe UI\', Roboto, \'Helvetica Neue\', Arial, \'Noto Sans\', sans-serif, \'Apple Color Emoji\', \'Segoe UI Emoji\', \'Segoe UI Symbol\', \'Noto Color Emoji\'; background-color: #ebedef; font-size: 14px; line-height: normal;\">Neighborhood Reporter does not &ldquo;sell&rdquo; Personal Information that on its own identifies you - such as your name or email address &ndash; without your permission. As discussed in the&nbsp;<a style=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: #007bff; text-decoration-line: none; background-color: transparent;\" href=\"http://www.neighborhoodreporter.com/privacy\">Privacy Policy</a>, Neighborhood Reporter does disclose or share other types of identifiers to our partners, advertisers and service providers, for use in providing their services, advertising purposes, or for improving and maintaining the quality and performance of the Neighborhood Reporter Service. The CCPA includes a very broad definition of &ldquo;sale,&rdquo; and under that definition some of such disclosures or sharing may be deemed to be a sale. Depending on how you use the Service and the permissions you have given Neighborhood Reporter, Neighborhood Reporter may &ldquo;sell&rdquo; the following categories of information (as defined in the CCPA) to third parties: identifiers; contact information; internet or electronic network activity information; geolocation information; commercial information; inferences, including advertising and content related inferences; and professional or employment related information.</p>\r\n<h3 style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0.5rem; font-weight: 500; line-height: 1.2; font-size: 16px; color: #212529; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \'Segoe UI\', Roboto, \'Helvetica Neue\', Arial, \'Noto Sans\', sans-serif, \'Apple Color Emoji\', \'Segoe UI Emoji\', \'Segoe UI Symbol\', \'Noto Color Emoji\'; background-color: #ebedef;\">Your California Privacy Rights</h3>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 12px 0px; color: #212529; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \'Segoe UI\', Roboto, \'Helvetica Neue\', Arial, \'Noto Sans\', sans-serif, \'Apple Color Emoji\', \'Segoe UI Emoji\', \'Segoe UI Symbol\', \'Noto Color Emoji\'; background-color: #ebedef; font-size: 14px; line-height: normal;\">If you are a California resident, you may request information about our disclosure of your personal information to third parties or affiliated companies for their direct marketing purposes. To make such a request, please contact us as set forth below. Please allow up to thirty (30) days for us to process your request. You may submit such a request once per year.</p>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 12px 0px; color: #212529; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \'Segoe UI\', Roboto, \'Helvetica Neue\', Arial, \'Noto Sans\', sans-serif, \'Apple Color Emoji\', \'Segoe UI Emoji\', \'Segoe UI Symbol\', \'Noto Color Emoji\'; background-color: #ebedef; font-size: 14px; line-height: normal;\">If you are a California resident, California law also provides you with the following rights with respect to your personal information:</p>\r\n<ul style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 1rem; color: #212529; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \'Segoe UI\', Roboto, \'Helvetica Neue\', Arial, \'Noto Sans\', sans-serif, \'Apple Color Emoji\', \'Segoe UI Emoji\', \'Segoe UI Symbol\', \'Noto Color Emoji\'; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ebedef;\">\r\n<li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 12px 0px; font-size: 14px; line-height: normal;\">The right to know what personal information we have collected, used, disclosed and sold about you.</li>\r\n<li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 12px 0px; font-size: 14px; line-height: normal;\">The right to request that we delete any personal information we have collected about you.</li>\r\n<li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 12px 0px; font-size: 14px; line-height: normal;\">The right to opt-out of the sale of your personal information.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 12px 0px; color: #212529; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \'Segoe UI\', Roboto, \'Helvetica Neue\', Arial, \'Noto Sans\', sans-serif, \'Apple Color Emoji\', \'Segoe UI Emoji\', \'Segoe UI Symbol\', \'Noto Color Emoji\'; background-color: #ebedef; font-size: 14px; line-height: normal;\">To submit a request for information about or deletion of your personal information, or to opt-out of sale of your personal information, please use the&nbsp;<a style=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: #007bff; text-decoration-line: none; background-color: transparent;\" href=\"https://privacyportal.onetrust.com/webform/bed72505-9a0f-49bf-adb9-a2e092d38e6c/1d73542b-2297-4315-ad4a-09f13e785c09\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\">Neighborhood Reporter Privacy Web Form,</a>&nbsp;or if you prefer contact us via email at&nbsp;<a style=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: #007bff; text-decoration-line: none; background-color: transparent;\" href=\"mailto:privacy@neighborhoodreporter.com\">privacy@neighborhoodreporter.com</a>&nbsp;or write to us at the address below.</p>\r\n<h1 class=\"st_About__Header\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 12px 0px; font-weight: 500; line-height: 1.2; font-size: 32px; color: #111111; font-family: Merriweather, Georgia, Times, serif; background-color: #ebedef;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: #212529; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \'Segoe UI\', Roboto, \'Helvetica Neue\', Arial, \'Noto Sans\', sans-serif, \'Apple Color Emoji\', \'Segoe UI Emoji\', \'Segoe UI Symbol\', \'Noto Color Emoji\'; font-size: 16px;\">Planck, LLC</span><br style=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: #212529; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \'Segoe UI\', Roboto, \'Helvetica Neue\', Arial, \'Noto Sans\', sans-serif, \'Apple Color Emoji\', \'Segoe UI Emoji\', \'Segoe UI Symbol\', \'Noto Color Emoji\'; font-size: 16px;\" /><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: #212529; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \'Segoe UI\', Roboto, \'Helvetica Neue\', Arial, \'Noto Sans\', sans-serif, \'Apple Color Emoji\', \'Segoe UI Emoji\', \'Segoe UI Symbol\', \'Noto Color Emoji\'; font-size: 16px;\">Attn: CCPA</span><br style=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: #212529; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \'Segoe UI\', Roboto, \'Helvetica Neue\', Arial, \'Noto Sans\', sans-serif, \'Apple Color Emoji\', \'Segoe UI Emoji\', \'Segoe UI Symbol\', \'Noto Color Emoji\'; font-size: 16px;\" /><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: #212529; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \'Segoe UI\', Roboto, \'Helvetica Neue\', Arial, \'Noto Sans\', sans-serif, \'Apple Color Emoji\', \'Segoe UI Emoji\', \'Segoe UI Symbol\', \'Noto Color Emoji\'; font-size: 16px;\">134 W. 29th Street, 11th Floor</span><br style=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: #212529; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \'Segoe UI\', Roboto, \'Helvetica Neue\', Arial, \'Noto Sans\', sans-serif, \'Apple Color Emoji\', \'Segoe UI Emoji\', \'Segoe UI Symbol\', \'Noto Color Emoji\'; font-size: 16px;\" /><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: #212529; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \'Segoe UI\', Roboto, \'Helvetica Neue\', Arial, \'Noto Sans\', sans-serif, \'Apple Color Emoji\', \'Segoe UI Emoji\', \'Segoe UI Symbol\', \'Noto Color Emoji\'; font-size: 16px;\">New York, NY 10001</span></h1>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 12px 0px; color: #212529; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \'Segoe UI\', Roboto, \'Helvetica Neue\', Arial, \'Noto Sans\', sans-serif, \'Apple Color Emoji\', \'Segoe UI Emoji\', \'Segoe UI Symbol\', \'Noto Color Emoji\'; background-color: #ebedef; font-size: 14px; line-height: normal;\">To opt-out or unsubscribe from Neighborhood Reporter email newsletters or other email communication, or update your email preferences, please click on the &ldquo;email preferences&rdquo; link at the bottom of any newsletter or other email, or send an email to&nbsp;<a style=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: #007bff; text-decoration-line: none; background-color: transparent;\" href=\"mailto:support@neighborhoodreporter.com\">support@neighborhoodreporter.com</a>. Information on how to turn off pop-up or push notifications from Neighborhood Reporter in your browser is available&nbsp;<a style=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: #007bff; text-decoration-line: none; background-color: transparent;\" href=\"#\">here</a>.</p>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 12px 0px; color: #212529; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \'Segoe UI\', Roboto, \'Helvetica Neue\', Arial, \'Noto Sans\', sans-serif, \'Apple Color Emoji\', \'Segoe UI Emoji\', \'Segoe UI Symbol\', \'Noto Color Emoji\'; background-color: #ebedef; font-size: 14px; line-height: normal;\">When you exercise these rights and submit a request to us, we may verify your identity by asking you to log in to your account if you have one with us or by asking for further information, such as your email address or other information, in order to verify your identity. We may also use a third party verification provider to verify your identity.</p>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 12px 0px; color: #212529; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \'Segoe UI\', Roboto, \'Helvetica Neue\', Arial, \'Noto Sans\', sans-serif, \'Apple Color Emoji\', \'Segoe UI Emoji\', \'Segoe UI Symbol\', \'Noto Color Emoji\'; background-color: #ebedef; font-size: 14px; line-height: normal;\">You have the right to designate an authorized agent to make any of the above requests on your behalf. Unless required otherwise by law, we will contact you using the contact information provided by your agent to confirm that you authorized the agent to act on your behalf.</p>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 12px 0px; color: #212529; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \'Segoe UI\', Roboto, \'Helvetica Neue\', Arial, \'Noto Sans\', sans-serif, \'Apple Color Emoji\', \'Segoe UI Emoji\', \'Segoe UI Symbol\', \'Noto Color Emoji\'; background-color: #ebedef; font-size: 14px; line-height: normal;\">You can opt-out of resale of your Personal Information by participants in the IAB&rsquo;s CCPA Limited Service Provider Agreement by clicking on this link to the&nbsp;<a style=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: #007bff; text-decoration-line: none; background-color: transparent;\" href=\"https://www.iabprivacy.com/optout.html\" rel=\"nofollow\">IAB&rsquo;s Signatory Identification List</a>&nbsp;and then opting-out by clicking the link(s) provided for the applicable participant(s).</p>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 12px 0px; color: #212529; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \'Segoe UI\', Roboto, \'Helvetica Neue\', Arial, \'Noto Sans\', sans-serif, \'Apple Color Emoji\', \'Segoe UI Emoji\', \'Segoe UI Symbol\', \'Noto Color Emoji\'; background-color: #ebedef; font-size: 14px; line-height: normal;\">Neighborhood Reporter will not discriminate against any consumer for exercising his or her rights under the CCPA. However, if you opt out of sale of your Personal Information or ask that we delete your Personal Information, your experience and use of the Service may be impacted as a result.</p>\r\n<h3 style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0.5rem; font-weight: 500; line-height: 1.2; font-size: 16px; color: #212529; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \'Segoe UI\', Roboto, \'Helvetica Neue\', Arial, \'Noto Sans\', sans-serif, \'Apple Color Emoji\', \'Segoe UI Emoji\', \'Segoe UI Symbol\', \'Noto Color Emoji\'; background-color: #ebedef;\">Contact Us</h3>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 12px 0px; color: #212529; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \'Segoe UI\', Roboto, \'Helvetica Neue\', Arial, \'Noto Sans\', sans-serif, \'Apple Color Emoji\', \'Segoe UI Emoji\', \'Segoe UI Symbol\', \'Noto Color Emoji\'; background-color: #ebedef; font-size: 14px; line-height: normal;\">If you have any questions about these California Disclosures or to request a copy of these California Disclosures in another format, please contact us at:</p>\r\n<h1 class=\"st_About__Header\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 12px 0px; font-weight: 500; line-height: 1.2; font-size: 32px; color: #111111; font-family: Merriweather, Georgia, Times, serif; background-color: #ebedef;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: #212529; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \'Segoe UI\', Roboto, \'Helvetica Neue\', Arial, \'Noto Sans\', sans-serif, \'Apple Color Emoji\', \'Segoe UI Emoji\', \'Segoe UI Symbol\', \'Noto Color Emoji\'; font-size: 16px;\">Maljon d/b/a Neighborhood Reporter Media</span><br style=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: #212529; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \'Segoe UI\', Roboto, \'Helvetica Neue\', Arial, \'Noto Sans\', sans-serif, \'Apple Color Emoji\', \'Segoe UI Emoji\', \'Segoe UI Symbol\', \'Noto Color Emoji\'; font-size: 16px;\" /><br style=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: #212529; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \'Segoe UI\', Roboto, \'Helvetica Neue\', Arial, \'Noto Sans\', sans-serif, \'Apple Color Emoji\', \'Segoe UI Emoji\', \'Segoe UI Symbol\', \'Noto Color Emoji\'; font-size: 16px;\" /><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: #212529; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \'Segoe UI\', Roboto, \'Helvetica Neue\', Arial, \'Noto Sans\', sans-serif, \'Apple Color Emoji\', \'Segoe UI Emoji\', \'Segoe UI Symbol\', \'Noto Color Emoji\'; font-size: 16px;\">1</span></h1>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 12px 0px; color: #212529; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \'Segoe UI\', Roboto, \'Helvetica Neue\', Arial, \'Noto Sans\', sans-serif, \'Apple Color Emoji\', \'Segoe UI Emoji\', \'Segoe UI Symbol\', \'Noto Color Emoji\'; background-color: #ebedef; font-size: 14px; line-height: normal;\">Email:&nbsp;<a style=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: #007bff; text-decoration-line: none; background-col